 cap from the skirt, thus releasing the contents of the storage chamber into the container. The flow tube extends above the storage chamber and terminates in a flow assembly having a cap sleeve movable between a closed position and a &#x201c;consume&#x201d; position in which the contents of the container can flow through the flow tube and out an opening in the cap sleeve.</p></abstract></us-patent-application>